Item Description
Dream of an African safari adventure with this beautiful comforter set. The stunning patchwork design borrows the spots, stripes and patterns of different animals for an exotic accent. Rich colors and a bold style make this a unique addition to your bedroom. Set includes comforter, skirt and shams (Twin set includes 1 sham). Machine wash. Polyester and cotton; imported. Available in Twin (63" x 86"), Full (76" x 86"), Queen (86" x 86"), or King (101" x 86").
